headline: Humana (NYSE:HUM) Debuts Cognitive Games to Engage Older Adults in Brain Health
summary: Humana (NYSE:HUM) recently launched the inaugural Humana Cognitive Games™ to promote brain health among older adults, coinciding with their tenth year sponsoring the National Senior Games. This initiative reflects the company's commitment to healthy aging. Despite these efforts, Humana’s share price experienced a 2% decline over the past month. This movement aligns with broader market trends, where major stock indexes remained relatively flat amid uncertainty from U.S. trade policy and...

headline: Healthcare & Life Sciences NLP Market Report 2025-2030, with Case Studies of CSL Behring, IQVIA, Atrius Health,  Linguamatics, Humana, Watson, Philips, and Amazon
summary: The NLP in healthcare & life sciences market is projected to grow from USD 5.18 billion in 2025 to USD 16.01 billion by 2030, at a CAGR of 25.3%. This growth is driven by the need to convert unstructured clinical data into actionable insights, enhancing clinical decision support.
